	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Fort Wayne</placeName> <date>Nov 23&#47;65</date></p>
				<p>Friend <addressee>I. Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p>In the Name of our <add>&#63;</add> congregation<lb/> we thank you heartily for your kind<lb/> wishes and the <sic>trubel</sic> you have taken<lb/> in our <sic>behalfe</sic>.  I have written to<lb/> <persName>Mr Jas Einstein</persName> for that Sephis<lb/> will direction how to send it.<lb/>  Our diversion seems to gain daily<lb/> friends on both <sic>sites</sic>&#44; that is to<lb/> say&#44; the feeling towards us by these<lb/> Reformers&#44; is very bitter&#44; and<lb/> I fear very much that the children<lb/> even on both <sic>sites</sic> will cultivate<lb/> bad feelings&#44; because <sic>the</sic> hear<lb/> it from their Parents.  I try all I can<lb/> to&#44; to <add>&#63;</add> these things and will<lb/> not permit it in my Family&#44; yet<lb/> such is the fact in other <sic>Familys</sic>.&#8212;</p>
				<p>Hoping this will reach you all well<lb/> with many kind regards</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Yours Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">J Laufirt<add>&#63;</add></persName></p>
		</body>
